snippet.title: Nexus Station - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
From the Social First team comes a new and exciting cross-platform Social Sandbox MMO, Nexus Station! 

Sign up for Early Access here: https://nexusstation.game/

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nexusstationgame/
Discord: https://discord.gg/nexusstation
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3224910/Nexus_Station
